{"tid":1542911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬唔好袋住先","createTime":"2019-09-05T04:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:58:42.000Z","uid":230905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"673af724647878eb6a65848699631b2a51fd02ca","tid":1542911,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:09:00.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母淋病，係度講廢話，同我地講法治，基本法，仲叫你相信監警會既中立性，根本就係共產黨一如以往既做法，換湯唔換藥，今次比佢過到骨，平息呢場運動，日後就更加難反抗，同烏克籣一樣，袋住先，加多幾條例，防止日後有類似咁既抗命運動<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201907/20190730130908_0_pcpu19080-2019-jul-30-026.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201907%2F20190730130908_0_pcpu19080-2019-jul-30-026.jpg&h=3b55edd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可 ，少一條都唔撚得，班狗唔撚解散，唔撚受制裁，仲在生既你，點對得住死咗既香港人，我地既手足！！<br />\n希望日後更多手足繼續出嚟抗命，如果依家你覺得咁既結果就滿意唔再出嚟，就正正中咗淋病想要既效果。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e04590b74fb45b4cc040106dea787aae7c004a2","tid":1542911,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"692986d2705eefd4f120de6bbe9d127506a7d5c2","tid":1542911,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5e